  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>The Villa Armas Cabins are self-catering cabins, with each cabin having their own equipped kitchen. The nearby supermarket is well stocked, and is open until 9pm (times to be confirmed locally).</p>
<p>If you would rather have your meals included, there is an optional pre-bookable half board supplement for buffet breakfast and three course buffet dinner, taken at Äkäs Hotel (Snow Elf) Hotel<a href="/{localLink:448b1a78-a915-4884-af75-2512a8008777}" title="Akas (Snow Elf) Hotel &amp; Alp Apartments"></a>, 150-250m away.</p>
<p> </p>]]></cateringDescription>
