  <description><![CDATA[<p><span>The Villa Armas Cabins are excellent value, well-equipped, semi-detached log cabins which are all conveniently arranged next to each other in a peaceful area. These cabins</span><span> are an excellent choice if you are part of a larger party wanting to book cabins close to each other, and for those of you who want the convenience of a short walk to the departure point of all the <a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/lapland-holidays/santa-breaks/resorts/laplandfinland">Santa Break</a> activities. </span></p>
<h2>Cosy log cabins </h2>
<p>One of the most authentic ways to see <a data-udi="umb://document/63d3751ab6044b7c82e72f82f4d64e39" href="/{localLink:umb://document/63d3751ab6044b7c82e72f82f4d64e39}" title="Lapland/Finland">Finnish Lapland</a> is to wake up in a warm and cosy log cabin. The cabins in <a data-udi="umb://document/8d7194d440db47e2b48d371f537fb9db" href="/{localLink:umb://document/8d7194d440db47e2b48d371f537fb9db}" title="Santa Breaks in Yllas">Ylläs</a> are a perfect place to stay for a short break as they are close to the village and excursion pick up point, so you can make the most out of your holiday.  Each cabin has its own private sauna and fireplace, perfect for warming up after a snowmobile safari or reindeer sleigh ride. The cabins are furnished with all the modern conveniences you'd need for a comfortable stay in the arctic circle.</p>
<h2><strong>Eat in or dine out</strong></h2>
<p><span>Our cabins all have an equipped kitchenette, making them a great choice for families looking to stay self-catered. There's an excellent, well-stocked supermarket in the village centre, along with cafes, shops and restaurants. You'll also have the choice to upgrade to half board, where you can enjoy hearty buffet style breakfasts and dinners in the Akas Hotel restaurant. </span></p>
<h2><span>Artic activities</span></h2>
<p><span>Lapland is one of the best places in the world to witness the Northern Lights and staying in the Villa Armas Log Cabins during the winter months provides an excellent opportunity to witness this natural phenomenon. The cabins are also a great base to enjoy our <a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/lapland-holidays/santa-breaks/excursions-activities/excursion-information">optional extra activitie</a>s such as snowmobiling, reindeer and husky rides and snow shoeing. Plus after a day of exploring, you can unwind in your cabin's private sauna or by the fireplace.</span></p>]]></description>
