  <locationDescription><![CDATA[<p>The Villa Armas cabins are dotted around a<span> peaceful area, around 150-250 metres from the Akas Hotel. </span></p>
<p>Guests may pay to use Äkäs Hotel pool and sauna (150-250m away)</p>
<p>The cabins are located 4 kilometres from the ski slopes and ski school, but the ski bus stop is outside the Akas Hotel, around 150-250 metres from the cabins.</p>
<p>The supermarket is around 800 metres from the cabins.</p>]]></locationDescription>
