  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Two bedroom + mezzanine cabins </strong>are around 45m² + 14m² and sleeps two to six people. These cabins have two twin bedrooms, a single bed in the mezzanine, and double sofa-bed in open-plan living room/kitchen. </p>
<p><strong>Cabin facilities</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Full equipped kitchen with oven, toaster, fridge, microwave, dishwasher, vacuum cleaner, coffee maker, iron and drying closet. </li>
<li>Sauna</li>
<li>Fireplace (small supply of wood included)</li>
<li>TV</li>
<li>One shower and WC</li>
<li>Central heating</li>
<li>One linen and towel set included, per person per week</li>
<li>Beds to be made on arrival</li>
<li>End of stay clean</li>
</ul>
<p> </p>
